---
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-20 md:py-28 text-white overflow-hidden leaf-pattern">
  <!-- Subtle accent -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-0 opacity-30">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-brand-500 blur-[140px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-brand-700 blur-[140px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 md:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 reveal">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-white/10 aspect-[5/4]">
          <img
            src="/images/mechanic-wrench.png"
            alt="Triton Hybrid technician servicing a hybrid vehicle"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Floating stat card -->
        <div class="hidden md:block -mt-10 ml-auto mr-8 lg:mr-0 lg:-mr-8 w-fit bg-white text-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-5 relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-600 text-white">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2 L3 7 V12 C3 17 7 21 12 22 C17 21 21 17 21 12 V7 L12 2Z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Meet Sal</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Owner &amp; Lead Technician</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 reveal" style="transition-delay: 120ms;">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-brand-400">Meet Sal — The Prius Whisperer</span>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight">
          <span class="text-brand-400">"Truly the Prius Whisperer."</span>
          <span class="block text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-300 mt-3">— Judy K., Google review</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-slate-200 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Sal doesn't dabble in hybrids — Priuses and hybrid batteries are <em>all</em> he does.
          Customers drive 30+ miles to see him, come back year after year, and recommend him
          to friends. Because when one customer was quoted <strong class="text-white">over $11,000</strong>
          by the dealership, Sal replaced the pack for a fraction of the cost. That's the kind
          of shop this is.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl border-2 border-brand-500 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-400">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Honest diagnostics, always</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                Every quote is backed by module-level testing and clear written findings.
                If you don't need a new battery, we'll tell you — and show you why.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl border-2 border-brand-500 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-400">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Dealership quality, fair prices</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                OEM-grade parts and specialist tooling at a fraction of dealer pricing.
                Most customers save $1,500 to $3,000+ on their repair.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl border-2 border-brand-500 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-400">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3h18v4a5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5V3z"/><path d="M7 21h10M12 12v9"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Trusted by 150+ 5-star customers</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                4.9 stars across 156 Google reviews. Our customers come back — and
                send their friends, family, and fellow Prius drivers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="#hero-form"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold shadow-brand hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Request a Free Quote
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:+17032619442"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white font-semibold ring-1 ring-white/20 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.37 1.9.72 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.35 1.85.59 2.81.72A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92Z"/></svg>
            Call (703) 261-9442
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
